\ ============================================================
\ Regime classification per PREDICTIONS-132.md.
\ ============================================================

\ Regime R: R_overall > 1.5 (× 1000 form: > 1500).
"R-overall-1000x" load 1500 > "regime-R?" store

\ Regime S: R_overall ∈ [0.8, 1.5] (× 1000 form: [800, 1500]).
"R-overall-1000x" load 800 >=
"R-overall-1000x" load 1500 <= * "regime-S?" store

\ Regime T: R_overall < 0.8.
"R-overall-1000x" load 800 < "regime-T?" store

\ Partition check.
"regime-R?" load "regime-S?" load + "regime-T?" load + "regime-count" store

