\ r9=1400, r10=2196 → 8 above 1.0.  Plus r1=0, r6=878 below.
"substrates-above-1" load 8 assert-eq

\ Max R is cycle_n10 = 7365 (×1000 form).
"max-R-1000x" load 7365 assert-eq

